caption.title: Related to Fig 1. Size-exclusion chromatography reveals a comparable size and elution profile between NS1-WT and NS1-N207Q.
caption.p: (A) Size-exclusion chromatography of 0.25 milligrams of purified and dialyzed DENV NS1-WT (black) and DENV NS1-N207Q (gray). (B) Western blot analysis, under denaturing conditions, revealing NS1 monomers from the indicated fractions from Panel A with NS1-WT on the top and NS1-N207Q on the bottom. Proteins are detected using an NS1-specific monoclonal antibody (7E11).
